          xml:id="pxp-nvdl">
   <refnamediv>
      <refname>pxp:nvdl</refname>
      <refname>cx:nvdl</refname>
      <refpurpose>Perform NVDL validation</refpurpose>
   </refnamediv>
   <refsynopsisdiv>
      <xi:include href="../declarations.xml" xpointer="xpath(/*/*[@type='pxp:nvdl'])"/>
   </refsynopsisdiv>
   <refsection>
      <title>Description</title>

<para>A step for performing <link xlink:href="http://www.nvdl.org/">NVDL</link>
(Namespace-based Validation Dispatching Language) validation over
mixed-namespace documents.</para>

<para>The <tag>pxp:nvdl</tag> step
<link xlink:href="http://exproc.org/proposed/steps/">is defined</link>
at <link xlink:href="http://exproc.org/"/>.</para>

<para>The names <tag>cx:nvdl</tag> and <tag>pxp:nvdl</tag> are
synonymous. The latter is preferred.</para>
   </refsection>
</refentry>